    USAGE

        fox [modules] [options]

    OPTIONS

        -b     --browser    Publishes the tests on localhost:7559
        -bv    --visit      Publishes the tests and visits automatically. PhantomJS required.
        -p     --port       Changes the default port number. [7559]
        -W     --no-watch   Do not watch file changes and run the tests automatically.

        -g     --grep       Run tests matching with given pattern
        -t     --timeout    Set test-case timeout in milliseconds [2000]

        -v     --version    Show version and exit
        -h     --help       Show help and exit
